    "html": "<section class=\"problem\" id=\"6-85\">\n<h2>6-85</h2>\n<div class=\"tagline\"><span class=\"pill\">Review/Preview</span> Sorted to Unit 2, Section 5: Linear Modeling with Data</div>\n<div class=\"audit\">Audit note: Uses data to sketch a scatterplot, residual plot, and correlation coefficient to evaluate a linear model.</div>\n<div><p>A human resources manager recorded the experience and hourly wage for a sample of 10 technology workers. <a class=\"etool-link\" href=\"https://www.desmos.com/calculator/i1cd7tvepx\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">6-85 HW eTool</a></p><table><tbody><tr><th><p> Experience (years) </p></th><td><p> $1$</p></td><td><p> $2$</p></td><td><p>$3$</p></td><td><p>$4$</p></td><td><p> $5$</p></td><td><p> $6$</p></td><td><p>$7$</p></td><td><p> $8$</p></td><td><p> $9$</p></td><td><p> $10$</p></td></tr><tr><th><p>Hourly Wage (\\$)</p></th><td><p>$12.00$</p></td><td><p>$13.25$</p></td><td><p>$14.00$</p></td><td><p>$16.00$</p></td><td><p>$17.00$</p></td><td><p>$18.00$</p></td><td><p>$19.50$</p></td><td><p>$21.00$</p></td><td><p>$22.00$</p></td><td><p>$23.25$</p></td></tr></tbody></table><ol class=\"lower-alpha\" type=\"a\"><li><p>Sketch a scatterplot showing the association between the wage and the years of experience. Describe the association.</p></li></ol><ol class=\"lower-alpha\" start=\"2\" type=\"a\"><li><p>Sketch the residual plot. Is a linear model appropriate?</p></li><li><p>What is the correlation coefficient? What does it tell you?</p></li></ol></div>\n</section>",
